        "TileImage": "$($repository 5cbb638f-3842-4920-af29-195988247473).Image",
        "Description": "Your mission is to eliminate these four men. They have formed a syndicate of terror and seized this opportunity to traffic classified lists from intelligence agencies. Mr Stephen Burns, a mole within the Spanish CNI, is at the heart of this operation. The leaders of the A.R.E.S. organisation must not be allowed to escape. We shall bring it all to an end in a single day. Good luck, 47.",
